{"tid":1700720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂][行動Po]十一月十一號朝早七點開花 全港被三罷","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T04:56:05.000Z","uid":227309,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"85def7798adceb813b649ac8b748e28d21f63181","tid":1700720,"uid":227309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"全世界 7:00 要準時聚到人<br />\n黨鐵路面都要人<br />\n禮拜一出得黎 就預左返唔到工 準備8:00打返公司話暴徒搞事阻街 返唔到工！<br />\n<br />\n行動如下 :<br />\n1. 夠人就即刻rb 唔駛講咁多 最好塞左巴士先 因為巴士司機大部份例牌唔會拆rb 通常熄匙落車<br />\n最有效塞死後面<br />\n2. Set完好走喇 黑唔黑衫自己定啦 其實著老西都冇問題 總之目的得一個 最緊要強制令全城癱瘓 罷到工<br />\n3. Set完就走 遊擊 如果popo出黎 就完成任務 變返打工仔 全城屌狗阻返工！<br />\n唔駛對峙 班狗到時分唔到邊班先係真係返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 運動黎到5個月 已經吹左好耐罷工 今次係強制性 靠大家準時！<br />\n只要11 11號開到個頭 keep住日日行動 咩行動日程表唔再需要 真正核彈已爆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4R8Wnav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4R8Wnav.jpg&h=23bb4c23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXn8dha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXn8dha.jpg&h=e005f486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DiwEjXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDiwEjXa.jpg&h=600e16a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DVj3aXcP9AOaDqXFAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DVj3aXcP9AOaDqXFAg&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=6085f81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DVj3aXcP9AOaDqXFAg</a><br />\n頻道link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=4ec9f9fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a>"},{"pid":"d758ef8aa0da75eacbc0004d858cf440a39c84f6","tid":1700720,"u